bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"III\" id=\"n75427.3\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> a great fish, perh. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">narwhal, Monodon monoceros,</tr_> or a kind of whale, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0099.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:2:7\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Str.\">Str.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.2.7</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}